'''帕東尼亞'''（{{lang-en|'''Padonia'''}}）為位在[[美國|美國]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[布朗縣_(堪薩斯州)|布朗縣]]的[[非建制地區|非建制地區]]<ref name=gnis/>。

==歷史==
1854年於帕東尼亞設立了第一個定居點<ref>{{cite book|title=History of the State of Kansas: Containing a Full Account of Its Growth from an Uninhabited Territory to a Wealthy and Important State|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5t09AQAAMAAJ&pg=PA739|year=1883|publisher=A. T. Andreas|page=739}}</ref>。此社區由最先定居者傑西·帕東（Jesse Padon）所命名<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Qi9cXyTWt9EC&pg=PA432#v=onepage&q&f=true | title=Kansas: A Cyclopedia of State History, Volume 2 | publisher=Standard Publishing Company | author=Blackmar, Frank Wilson | year=1912 | pages=432 | access-date=2016-03-14 | archive-date=2014-07-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707033207/http://books.google.com/books?id=Qi9cXyTWt9EC&pg=PA432#v=onepage&q&f=true | dead-url=no }}</ref>。1857年10月20日，郵政局於此地區開業，之後持續營業直到1933年5月31日歇業<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.postalhistory.com/postoffices.asp?task=display&state=KS&county=Brown&searchtext=&pagenum=2 | title=Brown County | publisher=Jim Forte Postal History | accessdate=15 February 2015 | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924115719/http://www.postalhistory.com/postoffices.asp?task=display&state=KS&county=Brown&searchtext=&pagenum=2 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

